{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-01-24",
 "title": "Back to Ghost Squadron",
 "summary": "In a Coruscant square, the former pilot Bazil McKenzie, now out of the Diplomatic Corps, tracks down Altair Quila, the new commander of Ghost Squadron, as she fends off a persistent pigeon by a statue. Bazil reveals he transferred out of diplomacy that very morning and admits he sought her out deliberately, hoping for a slot back in the squadron. Altair, who has left the executive officer position vacant since her own promotion, offers him the XO role outright, and he accepts. They share news of the still-missing former leader Andael and trade easy banter about uniforms and the ribbing the muster room will give him. The reunion ends with Bazil firmly reinstated as Ghost Squadron's second-in-command.",
